text: Tobias-Pascal Schultz (*25 June 1995) is a German sprint canoeist.Profile == Life == Tobias-Pascal Schultz is studying mathematics and sports at the University of Wuppertal, "Bergische Universität Wuppertal". He lives and trains in Essen. He trains together with other canoeists like Max Hoff or Max Rendschmidt . == Successes == 2016 EM bronze/3.place U23 K4 500m 2017 WM 7.place U23 K4 500m 2018 WM 10.place U23 K4 500m 2019 WM gold/1.place K4 1000m He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:German male canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak
